'''Bereg''' ({{FA|340}}) was [[Men|Man]] of the [[House of Bëor]].

== History ==
Bereg was the son of [[Baranor (son of Baran)|Baranor]], and a great-grandson of [[Bëor]] the Old.<ref>{{WJ|14}}, ''(i) The House of Bëor'', p. 231</ref> He led the unrest of [[Men]] at their camps at [[Estolad]]. In {{FA|369}} he led a thousand Men of the House of Bëor away southwards out of [[Beleriand]].<ref>{{S|West}}</ref>

His and his followers' fate is not known, but they reached [[Eriador]].<ref>{{S|Index}}, ''Bereg''</ref>

